Africa life expectancy: average - 48.9, minimal - 23.6, maximal - 76.4

Asia life expectancy: average - 60.1, minimal - 28.8, maximal - 82.6

Americas life expectancy: average - 64.7, minimal - 37.6, maximal - 80.7

Europe life expectancy: average - 71.9, minimal - 43.6, maximal - 81.8

Oceania life expectancy: average - 74.3, minimal - 69.1, maximal - 81.2

Asia has the largest maximal value and at the same time second-to-smallest minimal value. Africa has the smallest in each of the aggregated values.
